metadata.name: TWINS
metadata.description:
This artwork is created based on an architecture project that Leon Krykhtin worked on in the past.

The fluid lines of architecture merge with the landscape forming a coherent graphic composition transcending architecture from merely a building into a work of art.

The TWINS artwork is ready to print on high quality art paper with print quality 300 dpi. The print can be done on a size of up to 124x146 cm and can be framed for using in interior spaces.

The artwork can be also show on a digital screen up to 8k resolution. Digital size of the artwork is 8000x8642 pixels.
